my Awards|1962]]\n| ''[[Alcoa Premiere]]''\n| Outstanding Achievement in Original Music Composed for Television\n| {{nom}}\n| rowspan=6 | <ref>http://www.johnwilliams.org/reference/awards</ref>\n|-\n| [[15th Primetime Emmy Awards|1963]]\n| ''[[Alcoa Premiere]]''\n| Outstanding Achievement in Composing Original Music\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[20th Primetime Emmy Awards|1968]]\n| ''[[Heidi (1968 film)|Heidi]]''\n| Outstanding Achievement in Musical Composition\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| [[23rd Primetime Emmy Awards|1971]]\n| ''[[Jane Eyre (1970 film)|Jane Eyre]]''\n| Outstanding Achievement in Musical Composition\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| [[54th Primetime Emmy Awards|2002]]\n| [[74th Academy Awards]]\n| Outstanding Music Direction\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[61st Primetime Emmy Awards|2009]]\n| ''[[Great Performances]]''\n| [[Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Main Title Theme Music|Outstanding Original Main Title Theme Music]]\n| {{won}}<ref>{{cite news|title=Great Performances wins Primetime Emmy; John Williams interview|url=http://www.thirteen.org/insidethirteen/2009/09/15/great-performances-wins-primetime-emmy-john-williams-interview/|date=September 15, 2009|publisher=[[WNET]]|accessdate=January 21, 2013}}</ref>\n|- style=\"border-top:2px solid gray;\"\n|}\n\n===Golden Globe Awards===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:1em;\"| Year\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:35em;\"| Nominated work\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:40em;\"| Category\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:5em;\"| Result\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:1em;\"| Ref\n|-\n| [[30th Golden Globe Awards|1973]]\n| ''[[The Poseidon Adventure (1972 film)|The Poseidon Adventure]]''\n| [[Golden Globe Award for Best Original Score|Best Original Score]]\n| {{nom}}\n| rowspan=26 | <ref>http://www.johnwilliams.org/reference/awards</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=2 | [[31st Golden Globe Awards|1974]]\n| ''[[Cinderella Liberty]]''\n| Best Original Score\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| ''[[Tom Sawyer (1973 film)|Tom Sawyer]]'' <small>(with [[Richard M. S